    <line>You have read this strange &amp; terrific story,</line>
    <line>Margaret and <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">do</add>
      </mod> not you feel your blood con</line>
    <line>gealed with horror <delSpan spanTo="#c57-168.02" rend="strikethrough"/>Mine of<add
        place="sublinear">ten</add>did as he</line>
    <line>related it<anchor xml:id="c57-168.02"/><add><ptr target="#c57-168.03"/></add> – <del
        rend="strikethrough">When</del><add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">Sometimes</add> seized
      with <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">sudden</add>
      </mod> agony he</line>
    <line>could not continue <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">or</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">his tale, at others</add>
      </mod> his voice broken</line>
    <line>yet piercing <mod xml:id="c57-168.04" next="#c57-168.05">
        <del rend="strikethrough">described some of the scenes</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">uttered the words of which it is</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line><mod prev="#c57-168.04" xml:id="c57-168.05">
        <del rend="strikethrough">he had passed</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">composed.</add>
        <del rend="strikethrough">through</del>
      </mod> – His fine &amp; lovely</line>
    <line>eyes <mod type="additions" resp="#pbs">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">were now</add>
      </mod> lighted up <mod type="additions">
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">with</add>
      </mod> indignation <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">or</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">now</add>
      </mod> subdued</line>
    <line><!--note mod contains both hands: 
      is this considered a single intervention?--><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">by</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">to</add>
        <add place="superlinear"><metamark/>downcast</add>
      </mod> sorrow &amp; infinite wretchedness. Sometimes</line>
    <line>he commanded his countenance &amp; tones</line>
    <line>and related the most horrible incidents</line>
    <line>with a <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">smothered</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">tranquil</add>
      </mod> voice suppressing every</line>
    <line>mark of <del rend="strikethrough">indi</del> agitation – <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">and</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">then</add>
      </mod> like a vol</line>
    <line>cano bursting forth his face would sud</line>
    <line>denly change to an expression of the</line>
    <line>wildest rage as he shrieked <del rend="strikethrough">forth</del></line>
    <line>his imprecations <mod>
        <del rend="tetra-strike">of</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">on</add>
      </mod> his persecutor.</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>His tale is connected &amp; told with</line>
    <line>an appearance of the simplest truth</line>
    <line>yet I own to you my sister that the</line>
    <line>letters of Felix &amp; <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Maimouna</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">Safie</add>
      </mod> which he</line>
    <line>shewed me &amp; the apparition of the</line>
    <line>monster seen from our ship brought</line>
    <line>to me a greater conviction of the <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">fact</del>
        <add place="superlinear">truth</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line>than his asserverations <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">however earnest &amp;
